  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy a good buffet breakfast that includes homemade bread and jams made from the garden fruit.</p>
<p>You'll also get a free daily packed lunch to take with you.</p>
<p>The half board package includes an excellent four-course set menu for dinner, served in the hotel's Restaurant Elise. Tuck into delicious local specialities and seasonal produce.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
