  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Rooms</strong> are around 22m² and sleep two to four people (extra beds are put-up beds). These rooms have an ensuite with bath (with showerhead)</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Twin Rooms</strong> are around 22m² and sleep two to three people. These rooms are lake-facing and have a balcony and an ensuite with bath (with showerhead). Please note that some rooms may have restricted views of the lake due to protected trees</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are around 12m² and have an ensuite with shower</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>2pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A local tourist tax of approx. CHF3.00 per person per night is payable locally. Children aged 15 and under are exempt.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Steps into property: <strong>Yes</strong></li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
